Straight rows of keys are easy to guess

trans-unit.source: Short keyboard patterns are easy to guess

trans-unit.source: Use a longer keyboard pattern with more turns
trans-unit.target: Koristite duži šablon na tastaturi sa više prelaza.

trans-unit.source: Repeats like "aaa" are easy to guess
Repeats like "abcabcabc" are only slightly harder to guess than "abc"

trans-unit.source: Sequences like "abc" or "6543" are easy to guess

trans-unit.source: A word by itself is easy to guess
trans-unit.target: Samo jedna reč je lako za pogoditi.

trans-unit.source: Names and surnames by themselves are easy to guess
trans-unit.target: Samo ime i prezime je lako pogoditi.

trans-unit.source: Common names and surnames are easy to guess
trans-unit.target: Uobičajena imena i prezimena su laka za pogoditi.

trans-unit.source: Use a few words, avoid common phrases
trans-unit.target: Koristite nekoliko reči, izbegavajte uobičajene fraze.

trans-unit.source: No need for symbols, digits, or uppercase letters
trans-unit.target: Nema potrebe za simbolima, brojevima ili velikim slovima.

trans-unit.source: Avoid years that are associated with you
trans-unit.target: Izbegavajte godine koje su povezane s vama.

trans-unit.source: Avoid dates and years that are associated with you
trans-unit.target: Izbegavajte datume i godine koji su povezani s vama.

trans-unit.source: All-uppercase is almost as easy to guess as all-lowercase
trans-unit.target: Sva slova velikim ispisom su gotovo jednako laka za pogoditi kao i sva slova malim ispisom.

trans-unit.source: Reversed words aren't much harder to guess
trans-unit.target: Reči naopako napisane nije puno teže pogoditi.

trans-unit.source: Predictable substitutions like "@" instead of "a" don't help very much
trans-unit.target: Predvidive zamene poput "@" umesto "a" ne pomažu mnogo.

trans-unit.source: Add another word or two. Uncommon words are better.
trans-unit.target: Dodajte još jednu ili dve reči. Neobične reči su bolje.

trans-unit.source: Make your store comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
trans-unit.target: Osigurajte usklađenost svoje prodavnice s opštom uredbom o zaštiti podataka (GDPR).

trans-unit.source: There was an error on module uninstall. Please contact us through Addons website
trans-unit.target: Došlo je do greške prilikom deinstalacije. Molimo kontaktirajte nas kroz sajt tržišta ekstenzija

trans-unit.source: How can a customer retrieve all of his personal data?
trans-unit.target: Kako klijent / kupac može dobiti sve svoje osobne podatke?

trans-unit.source: From his customer account, a new tab called My Personal Data is available and your customer can retrieve all of his personal data collected by your shop and installed modules, in PDF or CSV format.
trans-unit.target: Iz svog korisničkog naloga, dostupna je nova kartica pod nazivom Moji lični podaci, gde vaš kupac može preuzeti sve svoje lične podatke koje je prikupipila vaša prodavnica i instalirani moduli, u PDF ili CSV formatu.

trans-unit.source: There is no consent confirmation checkbox in the contact form. Isn't this a requirement?
trans-unit.target: Nema potvrde pristanka u vidu polja za potvrdu na kontakt formi. Zar ovo nije obavezno?

trans-unit.source: No, it is not a requirement as the customer gives consent by clicking on the Submit message button. Only a message is required to give your customers more information about the use of personal data on your website. We are currently working on a new version of the contact form, it will be available really soon for your online store.
trans-unit.target: Ne, to nije obavezno jer korisnik daje pristanak klikom na dugme "Pošalji poruku". Samo je potrebna poruka koja pruža više informacija korisnicima o korišćenju ličnih podataka na vašem veb sajtu. Trenutno radimo na novoj verziji kontakt formulara koji će uskoro biti dostupan za vašu online prodavnicu.

trans-unit.source: How will a customer ask for all of his personal data to be deleted ?
trans-unit.target: Kako će korisnik zatražiti brisanje svih svojih ličnih podataka?

trans-unit.source: The customer will send a message from the contact form for any rectification and erasure requests, justifying his request.
trans-unit.target: Korisnik će poslati poruku putem kontakt forme s zahtevom za ispravkom ili brisanjem podataka, uz obrazloženje svog zahteva.

trans-unit.source: There is no Remove Data button in the customer account. Isn't this a requirement?
trans-unit.target: Nema dugmeta za brisanje podataka u korisničkom nalogu. Da li je ovo obavezno?

trans-unit.source:
No, the Remove Data button in the customer account is not an obligation. For the data erasure requests, your customers can request data removal only under certain circumstances, that is the reason why we decided not to include an automatic Remove Data button in their customer account.
They can, however, contact you anytime via your contact form, in this case, you can review their request and once you accept it, you will be able to remove their personal data directly in the configuration page of our Official GDPR Compliance module.
trans-unit.target:
Ne, dugme za brisanje podataka u korisničkom nalogu nije obaveza. Za zahteve za brisanje podataka, vaši korisnici mogu tražiti brisanje podataka samo u određenim okolnostima, zbog čega nismo uključili automatsko dugme za brisanje podataka u njihovom korisničkom nalogu.
Međutim, oni uvek mogu da vam se obrate putem kontakt formulara, u tom slučaju možete pregledati njihov zahtev i nakon što ga prihvatite, moći ćete da uklonite njihove lične podatke direktno na stranici konfiguracije našeg službenog GDPR Compliance modula.

trans-unit.source: How to remove the personal data of a customer?

If the request is valid, from the Personal Data Management tab of this module, any customer can be found by typing the first few letters of his name or email address in the search bar. Before deleting any data, we recommend you to download all the invoices of the involved customer. After deleting the data with the “Remove data” button, the customer’s orders can’t be legally deleted, they just won’t be linked to any account. This allows you to keep precise statistics of your shop.
trans-unit.target: Ako je zahtev validan, sa Personal Data Management kartice ovog modula, svaki korisnik može biti pronađen tako što ćete uneti nekoliko prvih slova njegovog imena ili adrese e-pošte u polje za pretragu. Pre nego što obrišete bilo kakve podatke, preporučujemo da preuzmete sve račune uključenog korisnika. Nakon brisanja podataka klikom na dugme "Remove data", korisnički nalozit se ne mogu zakonski obrisati, samo neće biti povezani sa bilo kojim nalogom. To vam omogućava da zadržite tačnu statistiku vaše prodavnice.

trans-unit.source: After removing all personal data of a customer from my database, what will happen to his orders?
trans-unit.target: Nakon što se uklone svi lični podaci kupca iz moje baze podataka, šta će se desiti sa njegovim porudžbinama?

trans-unit.source: Due to other legal obligations, his orders will still be stocked but they are no longer associated with the customer. Only the name, shipping, and billing information must be kept in the order details page for legal reasons, invoicing, and accounting. According to the Rec.30;Art.7(1)(c)
trans-unit.target: Zbog drugih pravnih obaveza, njegove porudžbine će i dalje biti sačuvane, ali neće biti više povezane sa kupcem. Samo ime, informacije o dostavi i naplati moraju biti zadržane na stranici sa detaljima porudžbine iz pravnih razloga, fakturisanja i računovodstva. Prema preporuci 30 i članu 7(1)(c) GDPR-a.
